  <!-- about  -->
  <section class="about section-space side-space">
    <div class="about-wrapper">
      <div class="about-img">
        <img src="./assets/imgs/about.webp" alt="" />
      </div>

      <div class="about-content">
        <p>
          The foundation of Sahyadri Hospitals was laid in 1994 with the
          establishment of Pune Institute of Neurology (PIN)—a modest
          16-bedded facility that evolved into Maharashtra’s first dedicated
          Neurology & Neurosurgery center. Over a decade of groundbreaking
          success paved the way for expansion, leading to the launch of
          Sahyadri Speciality Hospital in November 2004.
        </p>

        <p>
          Today, Sahyadri Super Speciality Hospital, Deccan Gymkhana, stands
          as a premier multispeciality hospital in Deccan, offering a
          225-bedded state-of-the-art facility. Combining medical expertise,
          advanced technology, and professional management, the hospital is
          committed to providing world-class healthcare solutions.
        </p>

        <p>
          What sets Sahyadri Super Speciality Hospital, Deccan apart is its
          distinguished team of renowned medical consultants, many of whom are
          recognized for their expertise on national and international
          platforms. These specialists work exclusively within the Sahyadri
          Group of Hospitals, ensuring dedicated, focused, and unparalleled
          medical care across various disciplines.
        </p>

        <p>
          The hospital’s excellence is further reinforced by a highly skilled
          and accountable paramedical and administrative team, whose
          unwavering dedication and commitment to quality consistently elevate
          patient care standards. Their continuous drive for improvement
          ensures that Sahyadri remains the best hospital in Deccan for those
          seeking comprehensive and specialized medical treatment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

